result.name: Yu Raku Tei Izakaya

reviews.text: Very nice place for Japanese food in the area. The food isn’t expensive and the quality is fine. Highly recommended the grilled salmon head which is huge proportion and truly delicious. The udon is also good to try.
The restaurant doesn’t look fancy or cozy in this location, but all food are fresh & tasty!
revisiting this resraurant from time to time. better reserve a table im advance.

Have been patronizing this place for nearly 20 years and for sure a landmark of Mei Foo.  Food is great and has a wide variety of menu items from expensive sake and sashimi to cheap beer and food like set meal of less than $100 per head.
Great Sushi. A la carte and seasonal dishes are delicious. Stewed radish is simple but surprisingly good

result.name: 友樂亭居酒屋

reviews.text: 跟朋友在友樂亭吃中午飯，訂了毛蟹腳刺身套餐，油甘魚鮮味，毛蟹可以，大約$120。

食材新鮮,價錢比較貴
也可說是一分錢一分貨
價錢略貴，味道佳及新鮮，座位少，建議如星期六及日晚上光顧便先訂位。
服務到位，面積比較細，需要提前訂位。食物味道還可以，價格可以接受。
